neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.se.association

Class AssociationAdd

  • java.lang.Object
    • neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.se.association.AssociationAddRem
      • neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.se.association.AssociationAdd
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Appendable

    public class AssociationAdd
extends AssociationAddRem
    Use this to specify attributes to add to a domain object in a domain update EPP command service element. The DomainUpdateCommand uses an instance of this to build the appropriate elements in order to request the addition of these attributes to a domain object.
